 本帖最后由 xmdhs 于 2020-1-27 14:04 编辑 

scoreboard players tag @a add a {SelectedItem:{id:"minecraft:diamond",tag:{display:{Name:"hello"}}}}
/scoreboard players tag @a add a {Inventory:[{Slot:-106b,id:"minecraft:diamond",tag:{display:{Name:"hello"}}}]}

scoreboard players tag @a add a {Inventory:[{Slot:103b,id:"minecraft:diamond",tag:{display:{Name:"hello"}}}]}

当然会影响，而且不好去做检测。建议用自定义一个 nbt 来检测这个物品。

这样给与 /give @a minecraft:diamond 1 0 {aa:1b}

然后这样检测 /scoreboard players tag @a add a {Inventory:[{Slot:-106b,id:"minecraft:diamond",tag:{aa:1b}}]}
